ktion zur speziellen Antibiotikatherapie. Ein unverzichtbarer Ratgeber für alle Orthopäden, die kompetent und sicher muskuloskelettale Infektionen behandeln wollen.  aThis book provides practical management guidelines for the diagnosis and treatment of musculoskeletal infections. It offers detailed presentations of diagnostic procedures and their explanatory power. Using algorithms, it presents a step-by-step therapy procedure for each diagnostic entity.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 21. Dez 2019) 4aGelenkinfekt. 4aOsteomyelitis. 4aPeriprothetischer Infekt. 4aSepsis. 4aWeichteildefekt. 70(DE-601)1042889140(DE-588)4026879-2aInfektionskrankheit2gnd 70(DE-601)1044594090(DE-588)4006318-5aBewegungsapparat2gnd 70(DE-601)1047039460(DE-588)4161650-9aInfektion2gnd 70(DE-601)10470456X0(DE-588)4075710-9aOrthopädische Chirurgie2gnd 7aMEDICAL / Orthopedics.2bisacsh1 aBraunschweig, Rainer.1 aFrommelt, Lars.1 aTiemann, Andreas Heinrich, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2016z9783110485103oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Medicine and Life Sciences 2016z9783110485295oZDB-23-DPM0 cEPUBz97831104735130 cprintz978311047315540uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783110474657423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783110474657.jpg  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_MDPM  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA12STME  aPDA14ALL  aPDA15STM  aPDA1ALL  aPDA3STM  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2016  aZDB-23-DPMb2016